# Installing Exercism on a Mac manually

1. Download the appropriate version of exercism based on your process architecture at the [releases page](https://github.com/exercism/cli/releases/latest).
2. Unzip and put the binary in your path.

After that, verify that it was installed properly by running:

```
exercism --version
```

